verbose_text: The lower levels of IL-10 and TGF-beta following GLP-2 treatment (with both ligands) noted in this study were similar to the results seen in previous studies, and this suggests that any effects GLP-2 may be exerting in the inflamed tissue are not likely due to an increase in these factors (XREF_FIG) [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
